        {
            "title": "布魯可暗盤飆逾七成  一手賺約13000元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鹹蛋超人概念股、拼搭角色類玩具生產商布魯可(00325)暗盤飆升，截至下午6時，輝立暗盤報104.3元，較招股價60.35元升43.95元或72.83%，一手不計手續費賺13155元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"布魯可集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/Bloks_Group-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"布魯可集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/Bloks_Group-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">布魯可集團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">耀才暗盤報103.4元，升43.05元或71.33%， 一手賺12915元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">布魯可周二﹙1 月7日﹚中午截止認購，市場數據顯示，主要券商孖展申購額達8827億元，單計孖展申購倍數超過6046倍，超購倍數打入港股歷史第三名，僅次毛記葵涌(01716)及草姬(02593)。公司具IP玩具消費概念，被視為下一隻泡泡瑪特(09992)。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14625222-%e5%b8%83%e9%ad%af%e5%8f%af%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be%e4%b8%83%e6%88%90-%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ba%e7%b4%8413000%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/Bloks_Group-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-01-09 18:15:26",
