            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "布魯可暗盤開升逾45%  現逾百元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鹹蛋超人股布魯可(00325)暗盤高開逾45%，現在多在平台暗盤價已逾百元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"布魯可集團初步招股書\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240520_FI_source-web_Bloks_Group.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"布魯可集團初步招股書\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240520_FI_source-web_Bloks_Group.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">布魯可集團初步招股書</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立暗盤開報88元，升45.82%，現報106元，升75.64% ; 耀才暗盤現報102.5元，升69.84%。</p>\n</div>",
